▶

▶ ツイート％s_hirono（非常上告-最高検察庁御中_ツイッター）％2018/09/17 12:16％ [[https://twitter.com/s_hirono/status/1041526205835436032>>https://twitter.com/s_hirono/status/1041526205835436032]]  
